SocksPort 9050
ControlPort 9051
CookieAuthentication 1
DataDirectory ./tor_data
Log notice file ./logs/tor.log
RunAsDaemon 0

# Security settings
SafeLogging 1
SafeSocks 1
TestSocks 1

# Exit policy (restrictive)
ExitPolicy reject *:*

# Circuit settings
MaxCircuitDirtiness 600
NewCircuitPeriod 30
MaxClientCircuitsPending 32
